## WHY NAT EXIST

What NAT does:

Allows many private devices

To share one public IP

####### Your laptop → Router (NAT) → Internet ########

Extra benefits:

Internal IPs are hidden

Direct inbound connections blocked

Slows basic attacks

Routing (ip route)

Tells system: “Where do packets go?”

Default gateway = exit door to internet

ip route

traceroute google.com

ss -rn
